race.comment: JAM PACKED (4) is unlucky to still be a maiden hitting the top-five in all nine starts to date and strikes a very winnable contest here. Has placed two of four over this distance range and should be right there when the whips are cracking. TWILIGHT STEPS (5) is knocking on the door of a maiden victory with consecutive runner-up finishes and only needs some luck navigating from the sticky draw to be playing a role in the finish. TINTAURA (11) has been thereabouts in recent efforts and the step-up in trip suits. Top-three contender. OLD FAITHFUL (2) has been well in the betting at the past couple and where there's smoke there's fire. Respect any market confidence. SHIP HAPPENS (10) rounds out the selections.
